			<h3 class="fw-title"><a name="48174217"></a><!-- ParagraphTitleStart -->Here, in the shadows behind this neon mausoleum... <!-- ParagraphTitleEnd --></h3>
			<div class="fw-text"><!-- ParagraphBodyStart --><p><img src="https://webzoom.freewebs.com/jarmsteadsnocturnes/dreamstime_m_18786267.jpg" border="0"></p>
<p>... You will find poems, short stories and novel excerpts showcasing the inventiveness and drama of modern thriller fiction from one of horror's rising new stars!</p>
<p>Moonlight and vampires, mean streets and serial killers, conference rooms and homicidal conspiracies, sorcerers, madmen, covert operatives and immortal monsters, come explore the tapestry of terror in the pages of Joseph Armstead's NOCTURNES!</p>
<p>Enjoy!</p>
